    "Although existing works make use of these techniques, there is still a lack on the feature selection strategies based on the new biomarkers identified in the medical community.",
    "The future works should take this into consideration so as to establish a correlation between biological significance and feature selection strategies.",
    "This leads to establishing explainability of the ML models.",
    "We have classified the existing works on CAD of the AD into two main categories.",
    "In the traditional ML model category, there are twenty one works and in the DL model category there are fifty nine works."
